data.description: ****PRICE REDUCED TO ACCOMODATE UPDATING DESIRES**** MILLION DOLLAR VIEWS for SALE, including HURRICANE SHUTTERS!  Owners are ready to sell this DIRECT oceanfront condo with unobstructed Atlantic ocean views., Year-round Florida living at its best can be enjoyed mornings to evenings with hours of relaxation on a wrap-around balcony.  This 3-bedroom 2 bath corner unit has natural light throughout, providing ocean views from every bedroom, living room, dining & kitchen.  Offering endless possibilities for rental income, the ultimate vacation get-a-way, or retirement home. Being sold furnished and has been well cared for, clean and move-in ready.  , on-site washer/dryer, and a special exterior patio & shuffleboard court, picnic area and firepit, complete with ocean views, breezes and the sounds of the waves coming ashore.                      *****SEE ADDITIONAL REMARKS***** This private and secure condo complex offers magnificent amenities including a refreshing pool, tennis/pickleball court, private parking garage, fitness center, social meeting room, on-site washer/dryer, and a special exterior patio & shuffleboard court, picnic area and firepit, complete with ocean views, breezes and the sounds of the waves coming ashore.  Experience a pampered southern lifestyle with peace, privacy & security, located in the heart of Flagler Beach Florida. Located on the 7th floor, this condo is high and dry with spectacular views of the Atlantic ocean and intracoastal and is safe and secure with protective hurricane shutters.  Local restaurants, shopping, outdoor recreation, Flagler Beach Pier and state parks are numerous and nearby.  Located on scenic A1A historic highway with easy commutes to historic St. Augustine, Daytona Beach, Orlando, and I-95.  *****VERY IMPORTANT***** DO NOT TOUCH THE STORM ELECTRIC SHUTTERS UNDER ANY CIRCUMSTANCES!!!  THEY ARE IN PERFECT WORKING CONDITION AND CAN BE TESTED BY A LICENSED INSPECTOR AT THE APPROPRIATE TIME.  THE OWNERS HAVE CAMERAS AND IF THE SHUTTER MOTORS ARE DAMAGED, THE REALTOR WILL BE LIABLE FOR DAMAGES.
